Class UserManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.inrix.sdk.UserManager

  • public class UserManager
extends Object
    Provides access to the API to create users and authenticate existing users.

      • signInWithOAuth

        public ICancellable signInWithOAuth(@NonNull
                           UserManager.OAuthSignInOptions options,
                           @NonNull
                           UserManager.OAuthSignInListener listener)
        Sign in using third-party OAuth credentials. Use UserManager.signOut(UserSignOutListener) to sign out.

        Note that it is not necessary to create an account via UserManager.create(UserCreateOptions, UserCreateListener) when signing in with OAuth credentials.

        Parameters:
        options - OAuth sign in options.
        listener - Response listener that is called when user signed in.
        Returns:
        An instance of ICancellable to cancel the request.
